---
Title: Laughing at the Word Two
By: 6e692c9a-52ef-49c0-a8c5-4ab5e733a7cd
Source:
  - Title: The Gift
    Page: 84
---
Only

That Illumined One

Who keeps
Seducing the formless into form

had the charm to win my
Heart.

Only a Perfect One

Who is always
Laughing at the word
Two

Can make you know

Of

Love.
